## 8. Computational Notes

| Operation | Approx. time | Notes |
|-----------|-------------|-------|
| DEM download (1 arc-sec, 0.5° × 0.5°) | 5–20 s | Cached after first run |
| SLR projection fetch | 2–5 s | Cached per station + scenario |
| `predictCoastline` (1000×1000 grid) | < 1 s | Vectorized MATLAB ops |
| `visualizeCoastline` | 1–3 s | Depends on GPU/graphics driver |

For bounding boxes larger than ~1° × 1°, reduce `Resolution` to 3 arc-seconds to keep the DEM under 3000 × 3000 cells and maintain interactive response times.
